{"tid":1746991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA觀測到史上最強伽瑪射線暴　1秒超越太陽百億年能量","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T09:19:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e51d528608667e8f3a95c3359049fcd922f65987","tid":1746991,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCn99sU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCn99sU.jpg&h=8932e46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）周四（21日）宣布，哈伯太空望遠鏡（Hubble SpaceTelescope，HST）於今年1月14日觀測到宇宙已知最強烈的「伽瑪射線暴」（Gamma RayBrust，GRB）爆發。1秒鐘內噴發的能量，超過太陽整個生命週期（約100億年）散發的能量。<br />\n <br />\nNASA指，全球逾20個天文台於1月14日（台灣時間1月15日上午），都觀察到異常明亮且持久的伽瑪射線暴。觀測時間長達40分鐘。這場名為「GRB 190114C」的大爆發，發生於距地球45億光年的星系中央（天爐座方向），伽瑪射線能量範圍為2000億至1兆電子伏特（<br />\neV），是我們周圍「可見光」光子能量的1兆倍（可見光的光子能量僅1eV），龐大威力是人類觀測史上首見。研究人員分析，原因可能是因為爆發發生於密集的星系中心，令威力龐大。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《獨立報》、日本天文網站《Sorae》報導，伽瑪射線暴是宇宙中威力最強大的爆炸；這次爆發的成因，研判是大質量（太陽的約100倍重）恆星崩壞、演化為黑洞時，朝恆星的兩極放出電漿噴流（plasma jet）而產生。"},{"pid":"a23010fdce5ca4c22962ef7cf57ed5081de570c6","tid":1746991,"uid":99930,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"都係打唔贏香港警察"},{"pid":"333fc05fb12ea21db88837cb0377d0fdb5fb2214","tid":1746991,"uid":165749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a23010fdce5ca4c22962ef7cf57ed5081de570c6","tid":1746991,"uid":99930,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"都係打唔贏香港警察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"香港警察只是一個笑話"},{"pid":"3ad6183016ea1e26d02fce6697fe8dc7c45cf923","tid":1746991,"uid":61967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR1yZxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR1yZxc.jpg&h=526b70c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票呀，香港人！</span>"},{"pid":"23031070027d6712d5c00d3ecfb66b43951c366e","tid":1746991,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔明講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲投票喇"},{"pid":"d1d045f3d21bcda7ea0585d65aa734fa738cf1ef","tid":1746991,"uid":230054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d9149bd7c0cd248a0a124ea6b6f63b318e1f4c","tid":1746991,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"射向地球唔該"},{"pid":"0b67ed98ed07443c9a4c7d7098361b93c6cf81c8","tid":1746991,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"諗起睇書講黑洞如果識爆炸，都會發出高能射線<br />\n<br />\n而星系中間通常會有黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}